    public interface Exportable
extends java.rmi.Remote, java.io.Serializable
    This interface represents exportable object which has export(int) method and unexport() method. An exportable object is similar to AutoCloseable object except that the #finalize() method of exportable object should call its unexport() method (instead of calling AutoCloseable.close() method).
    Version:
    12.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
